Blah. Forgot about this. Add this on to my last post with Zardus.

::Zardus::

Zardus looks to his left at the exchange of fire between Inzola and 
Demmos, activating his comm-link to the four bots involved.

"Stop firing," he says to them, "You're allied now. I'll be glad to 
listen to any objections you have later, but after the battle."





--- In nbwrpg@egroups.com, "THECODE" <thecode@p...> wrote:
> Inzola looked away from Koj and she had heard it all, Deemos's 
group, the Alliance let them in? How was it possible? The Alliance 
had betrayed her!
> 
> Deemos looked from behind Gigas and smiled evilly at Inzola. Inzola 
instinctively fires at Deemos. The shot hits Gigas, but even though 
it was fired by Inzola, Gigas doesn't pay attention. Stranato was 
just staring, dumbfounded the whole time. Deemos comes out from 
behind Gigas and angrily glares at Inzola, who promptly shoots him in 
the head. Stranato stares dumbfounded at Inzola. Deemos, on the 
ground, was looking on in shock at Inzola...
